The '''Blue Light''' was a tavern that only served liquor in the [[Corellian Sector (Nar Shaddaa)/Legends|Corellian Sector]] of [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. The establishment was owned by [[Mich Flenn]], a former [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]]. The interior was kept dark, and the walls were decorated with [[Holoposter|holo-posters]] of [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] cities and natural wonders. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] frequented the Blue Light and intially met former girlfriend [[Salla Zend]] there.

